This package provides Python libNeuroML, for working with neuronal models specified in NeuroML (http://neuroml.org)

Documentation is available at http://readthedocs.org/docs/libneuroml/en/latest/

The project home page is at http://neuroml.org/neuroml2 (this needs to be updated to point to Github...)

For installation instructions, see http://readthedocs.org/docs/libneuroml/en/latest/how_to_contribute.html

For some thoughts on the overall scope of the project, see https://github.com/NeuralEnsemble/libNeuroML/blob/master/ideas/padraig/ScopeOfProject

